data.description: Beautifully built and completed in 2019, this newer home sits on a corner lot of 2.88 acres and has so much to offer! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath gem is located in a desirable neighborhood behind Vidalia High School. The interior boasts grand vaulted ceilings and an open-concept floorplan. Just inside from the double garage is a large mudroom with ample storage, access to washer & dryer, and pex water system. The oversized primary bedroom is also located on this wing and gleams custom barn doors, high ceilings, and a walk-in closet. White cabinets line the kitchen with views of the open dining and living room. Plenty of room for barstools and a large table to host family and friends! An alcove just off the living/dining room leads to the secondary bedrooms and guest bathroom. The exterior boasts ample space and a covered back porch with ceiling fan, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Call today to schedule your private showing!
